<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Tales/Troubles of Hyrule; The legend of Zelda module. <p>
Just a few ideas. 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 There woud be no race/class choices, you would play as Link. He would have pretty good skills at most things though. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 The map would be changed to Hyrule and towns and dungeons would change too. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 All dungeons would have a boss in a special level which can not be exited until the boss is defeated. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 There aren't enough Zelda monsters to completely re-write them, but some new monsters and uniques could be added. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Sauron and Morgoth are changed to Ganondorf and Ganon of course! 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 More special levels, some with puzzles to solve. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Re-do items so that finding any armour, scrolls etc. are rare but gold it plentiful. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Weapons are not generated except on special occasions.  
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Add time-bombs! Also, make the bow much more powerful. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Empty bottles must be made more rare and useful. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Various special items (artifacts?) such as the grappling hook, deku leaf etc. 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<p>
I'm guessing most of these would be almost impossible to add/change but it was just a thought. 
</p>
